#: ../../source/How-To-Guides/DDS-tuning.rst:49
msgid ""
"Reducing this parameter’s value also reduces the window of time where no "
"fragments are received. The parameter is global for all incoming fragments, "
"so the feasibility of reducing its value needs to be considered for every "
